  "markup": "\u003Cp\u003ECan we only offer help with photobiomodulation after there\u0027s been an insult to the tissue? \u003C/p\u003E\r\n\u003Cp\u003EIn the November webinar we are going to talk extensively about prevention and something we call Laser Prehab. You will be fascinated to find out that there\u0027s actually quite a bit that can be done before tissue is compromised. If you know that you\u0027re going to have surgery, or perform some strenuous activities then photobiomodulation could play a pivotal role in the how the tissue responds to an insult, enabling you to \u0026ldquo;stack the deck\u0026rdquo; in your favor. Learn how to master these techniques in our November webinar. \u003C/p\u003E\r\n\u003Cp\u003EJoin Dr. Chris Carraway for an in-depth look at Laser Prehab. \u003C/p\u003E"
}]]></Value>
